{"tid":1876141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[大躍進] 好消息！寧夏累計治愈22人，治愈率達41.5%！","createTime":"2020-02-12T08:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T09:21:29.000Z","uid":53062,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2349377f54d10ef9c7de8236be44dbddb791ade8","tid":1876141,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img2.utuku.china.com/640x0/news/20200212/5209b3ee-8bfd-46d5-8380-9eed0eaf8ec0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.utuku.china.com%2F640x0%2Fnews%2F20200212%2F5209b3ee-8bfd-46d5-8380-9eed0eaf8ec0.jpg&h=9d6b42d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2月11日下午，自治區第四人民醫院再次傳來好消息，又有8名確診患者治愈出院！年齡最大的患者76歲，最小的11歲。<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情發生以來，寧夏舉全區之力組建自治區診療專家組，對確診患者實施定點治療、專家治療、免費治療，同時針對每位確診患者進行個案病情精準分型，一人一案、一人一策，採取中西醫結合方式，科學救治。<br />\n<br />\n截至目前，我區確診患者出院人數達到22名，確診病例治愈率達到41.5%。 （寧夏日報記者尚陵彬）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廿一世紀大躍進，大家鬥虛報確診數字、治癒率、死亡率<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458503630287f13f059e9f3b08b81458a2d93859","tid":1876141,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"解封武漢未？"},{"pid":"c924da5602555736b824c6cf87ec31232edb9f1e","tid":1876141,"uid":166729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"醫療強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83802312a3379600cc67e0df1b09c535190c56b","tid":1876141,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"香港今日都有2名確診者可以出院，gd news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fc7e9626de5134aedf81ab2b4d3b4a8d8fbf3d","tid":1876141,"uid":86898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>定點治療、專家治療、免費治療</blockquote><br />\n即係訓係醫院，搵個醫生睇症，免你診金"},{"pid":"d65a54f59d395896f5877d9a416095149e543fa9","tid":1876141,"uid":228143,"